title: Roman Reigns will leave WWE if he doesn’t beat John Cena | FRIDAY NIGHT SMACKDOWN | WWE ON FOX
author: WWE ON FOX
description:
Roman Reigns and John Cena came face to face one last time on Friday Night SmackDown before clashing at SummerSlam. The Tribal Chief raised the stakes, threatening to leave the WWE if he doesn’t maintain the Universal Championship.
